            bindings = <
       &kp Q       &kp W            &kp F        &kp P        &kp G        &kp J    &kp L             &kp U        &kp Y              &kp SEMI
       &mt LGUI A  &mt LALT R       &mt LCTRL S  &mt LSHFT T  &kp D        &kp H    &mt LEFT_SHIFT N  &mt LCTRL E  &mt LEFT_ALT I     &mt LEFT_GUI O
